HEADWORD: no-show
<hw>no-show</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>someone who shirks a
duty.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nonattender, truant.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who is expected to attend a gathering but
does not come.</def> <specif>Specifically,</specif> <def>a person who
buys a ticket to a game or other entertainment and does not
attend.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

